{"title":"缅怀贺帅","authors":["张平化"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":3,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅怀贺帅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张平化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八一年三月是贺龙同志诞生八十五周年谨吟诗三首聊表纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马缚苍龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转战东西南北中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凛冽风霜知劲草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难岁月识英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条鞭杆当前哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两把菜刀立首功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命勋劳载史册"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永垂不朽万年红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北伐凯歌旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江逆浪掀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义旗飘赣粤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战号震湘黔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"策马川康道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会师甘陕边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹心向北斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红遍九重天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善恶终归辨是非"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心国法眼恢恢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇冤昭雪军民快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩气长存日月辉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}